<td align="center"><b>
<i>Andrena nigra</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Provancher, 1895</font></b><br>
<small><i>Andrena griseonigra </i>Cockerell, 1905; <i>Andrena subtristis </i>Cockerell, 1905; <i>Andrena &#40;Melandrena&#41; griseonigra </i>Cockerell, 1905; <i>Andrena &#40;Melandrena&#41; nigra </i>Provancher, 1895; <i>Andrena &#40;Melandrena&#41; subtristis </i>Cockerell, 1905</small><p>
